Release:        2%{?dist}
License:        MIT
Vendor:         Microsoft Corporation
Distribution:   Azure Linux
Group:          System Environment/Base
URL:            https://aka.ms/mariner

ExclusiveArch:  x86_64

Requires:       bash
Requires:       ca-certificates
Requires:       chrony
Requires:       cpio
Requires:       cryptsetup
Requires:       curl
Requires:       dbus
Requires:       elfutils-libelf
Requires:       filesystem
